Package team.cascade.spout.makememod.exceptions

Exception Summary
ConfigNotAvailableException Exception which is thrown by the CommentConfiguration when the configuration is not available.
ConfigNotInitializedException Exception which is thrown by the CommentConfiguration when the configuration is not initialized.
NoPermissionException Exception which is thrown by the Permissions enum
WrongClassException Exception which is thrown by the Config enum when the class which is being set is different to the class which is already stored in the enum
